parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Battery Drain and Electrical System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and electrical system issues can cause the vehicle to stall or become inoperable, leading to safety risks, inconvenience, and financial losses.
symptoms: The battery drains completely and inconsistently
the vehicle stalls or becomes inoperable
warning indicators illuminate
power window switches fail to operate
the engine fails to restart
and the SRS warning indicator remains illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fan control module can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, safety risks, and financial losses.
symptoms: The air conditioner does not work properly
the engine overheats
and the cooling system function is lost.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Ignition Lock Switch and Starter Switch Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition lock switch and starter switch can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to safety risks, inconvenience, and financial losses.
symptoms: The ignition key will not turn to unlock the steering column
the steering column remains locked
the vehicle cannot be started
and the ignition lock switch and starter switch fail to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to slip gears, leading to loss of control and potential accidents. It can also result in costly repairs and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a shaking motion
loud clunking noises from the front end
excessive vibration/shaking in the drive train
transmission slips gears
failure to shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature failure of drive axles can create an unstable driving incident, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Loud clunking noises from the front end
excessive vibration/shaking in the drive train
drive axles worn out prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the transmission valve body can cause the transmission to slip gears, leading to loss of control and potential accidents. It can also result in costly repairs and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Excessive vibration/shaking in the drive train
transmission slips gears
failure to shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Issues with the engine management software can cause the transmission to slip gears, leading to loss of control and potential accidents. It can also result in costly repairs and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission slips gears
failure to shift gears properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rough transmission shifting can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Rough shifting between 1-2 gear and 5-6 gear
rough downshifting from 3-2 and 2-1 gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fuel pump leak can cause a strong fuel smell, which can lead to a fire hazard, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Strong fuel smell inside and outside the vehicle
especially in hot climates
fuel leak from the fuel sending unit under the back seat.
